name: Lost Ones
description:
Created with canvas. Generative text and output. Inspired by polaroid film that failed to develop.

This project uses your wallet hash as a seed to generate a unique piece for each collector. Once minted it will use your user hash, but currently uses a random hash for output.

Click the `ipfs` link to view outputs. Click anywhere on the page to refresh with a random hash.

Press:
- 'p' to show the lost memory
- 's' key to show seed.
